The way we did EDH was that there’s two prizes. One goes to the winner of the game, and one goes to the person who did the coolest play, and it can’t be the same person. When deciding the coolest thing, everyone votes for someone other than themselves.
5$ entry, you get a slice of pizza, and a pack of the set in standard
Pretty simple, not too many prizes, everybody has fun
